    179               B-4. Aggregate trade indices (value, price and quantity)
    180               B-5. Trade balance indices
    181               B-6. Terms of trade (ToT) decomposition
    182          11.  Welfare measurement and decomposition
    183    
    184       Welfare summary and post-sim calculations:
    185          C. Welfare decomposition summary
    186          D. Volume changes (GTAPVol)
    187          E. Data balance checks
